text: show ad Police pull body of a man in his 40s from a lake at the University of Birmingham in front of horrified students The body of a man in his 40s has been found in a lake on a university campus It was found on grounds of the University of Birmingham at 3.30pm yesterday West Midlands Police said death does not involve university staff or students
